; Regression test for issue #854: -v maps to --verbose, it should map to --version (BZ#854)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/854
; Bug: -v flag currently enables --verbose mode instead of showing --version info.
; When fixed, "ledger -v bal" should output version info and exit, not a balance report.

2024/01/01 Test transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test -v bal 2>/dev/null
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
